---
title: Creamy Mushroom, Thyme & Leek Fettuccine with Pine Nut Pangrattato
description: It is that time of the week again, pasta night and we’re here to twist things around. Herbs and mushrooms are a must in any pasta dish, add leek and fragrant thyme, then garnish with a nutty pangrattato for something a bit different and definitely delicious.
